room_title: Escape room "Carnival" by Real and Wild Entertainment in Breckenridge
room_address: 224 S. Main Street Ste. 5, Breckenridge, CO 80424
room_description: You are a local police investigator who has been chasing the notorious gangster Jankin Badger for the past two years. You just received an anonymous tip that Jankin may be posing as the Bearded Lady in the Carnival! But before you can make an arrest you'll need proof! The clock starts counting down as she steps on stage, and you step onto the scene. Will you escape before she returns?
